PrecisSTORAGE CHARGES REMISSION ORDER, 1993 - which provides for the remission of unpaid storage charges imposed under the Storage of Goods Regulations (from September 18, 1986 to September 14, 1988) after the third consecutive day on which goods were stored at a customs office, rather than after the third business day, as intended.
RegistrationRegistration: SI / 1993-0080 Publication Date: 1993-06-16
Attachments
precis:
STORAGE CHARGES REMISSION ORDER, 1993 - which provides for the remission of
unpaid storage charges imposed under the Storage of Goods Regulations (from
September 18, 1986 to September 14, 1988) after the third consecutive day
on which goods were stored at a customs office, rather than after the third
business day, as intended.
